# Local-development-only tools that must NOT be deployed to Vercel.
#
# api/ingest-local OCRs a folder of scanned images read from the local disk
# (process.cwd() + a dynamic folderPath). It cannot run on Vercel's read-only,
# ephemeral serverless filesystem, and its dynamic fs tracing bloats the function
# bundle past Vercel's 250 MB limit — breaking the whole build. Excluded here.
src/app/api/ingest-local
